Setting val_fold to something invalid (i.e. something not in 0 -> 4) puts all the data into the train set.

{% raw %} 
dls = get_dls_all_in_1(TEST_DATA_PATH, val_fold=-1, bs=3)
len(dls.train_ds), len(dls.valid_ds)
